# ============================================================
# DREAMCHAMBER — MC96 Ecosystem
# CONSTITUTIONAL MEDIA BLOCK
# No audio. No video. No binaries. Code and docs only.
# Media lives on THE AQUARIUM (34TB external) only.
# Never on GOD system drive. Never in version control.
# ============================================================

